Hey!

This one didn't apply, because your client wrapped two long lines.

[...]
> +    ahead=$(git rev-list ${hook_com[branch]}@{upstream}..HEAD 2>/dev/null | wc 
> -l)
[...]
> +    behind=$(git rev-list HEAD..${hook_com[branch]}@{upstream} 2>/dev/null | wc 
